sentences: Angaleena Loletta McCoy Presley (born September 1, 1976) is an American country music singer-songwriter.
She is a member of the country trio Pistol Annies, which was formed in 2011 with Miranda Lambert and Ashley Monroe, and has released two solo albums, American Middle Class (2014) and Wrangled (2017).
